Our code is GroupSix.java and Microphone.java

To run our program:
1. Install required OpenNI/NITE programs
2. Run the NiUserTracker sample to make sure a user is properly recognized
3. Compile GroupSix.java
4. Run GroupSix
5. Hero makes a wave or click motion, this will trigger getAudio() for the Snakeman
6. Snakeman has 10 seconds to make a loud enough noise

Also, at step 4, oni files can be used by entering their path as a command line argument
